## Verification
The defined invariants align with:
- **GAAP/IFRS Principles**: Revenue/Expense recognition and dual-entry consistency.
- **Forensic Accounting Standards**: Immutable audit logs and hash-based integrity.
- **Modern Ledger Design**: Versioning instead of mutation.
